data.description:
Welcome to 818 West St, where charm meets modern comfort! This delightful 2-bedroom home boasts a cozy fireplace in the living room, perfect for those chilly evenings.
Experience the joy of indoor-outdoor living with a spacious fenced-in backyard, ideal for entertaining friends and family or simply enjoying your morning coffee in peace. Brand-new 5' shower recently installed and has never been used. 
Convenience meets functionality with a two-stall detached garage, providing ample space for parking, storage, or even a workshop—your options are endless. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, close to Muskegon Community College, shopping and restaurants. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, with easy access to amenities and attractions. Don't miss out on making 818 West St your next home sweet home! Buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information.
